Articles.Content:
When ever I put on struts on a craft always find my self singing: Strut, Strut, Strut it Up! Stru,

Stru, Stru, Stru, Strut it Up!

I even made a extended a Song!

Strut, Strut, Strut it up!

Stru,Stru,Stru, Stru, Strut it Up

Strut, Strut, Strut it up!

Stru,Stru,Stru, Stru, Strut it Up!

When your aircraft are wiggiling and wagalling

When your rockets fly, then explode

When you need a help flying, and don't know what to do,

Then Strut, Strut, Strut, it Up!

Strut, Strut, Strut it up!

Stru,Stru,Stru, Stru, Strut it Up

Strut, Strut, Strut it up!

Stru,Stru,Stru, Stru, Strut it Up!

When your wings are high and engines are low

When your rockets hover low

When you lose your Interplanatary Stage

Then Strutting is the way to Go!

Strut, Strut, Strut it up!

Stru,Stru,Stru, Stru, Strut it Up

Strut, Strut, Strut it up!

Stru,Stru,Stru, Stru, Strut it Up!

Rockets, Rovers, Rovers and Planes

Train, Bases and things that are pains,

VTOLS, SSTOS

Whatever the size, or engine power

Struts are your main Super Power!

Strut, Strut, Strut it up!

Stru,Stru,Stru, Stru, Strut it Up

Strut, Strut, Strut it up!

Stru,Stru,Stru, Stru, Strut it Up!

Everybody now!

Strut, Strut, Strut it up!

Stru,Stru,Stru, Stru, Strut it Up

Strut, Strut, Strut it up!

Stru,Stru,Stru, Stru, Strut it Up!!!!!!!!
